eplay.com-pics-Wythe.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> An idea</span><hr size=1> No crtitique meant for those that have been leading dragon raids of late, but as a project, with some long-term goals for us, I'd love to see someone from the SGA lead one--that is, for us to host an open raid, with loot rules and reiumbursements for clerics and so on.<br>
<br>
I am a poor choice to lead anything like this, as I am still unsure how to Get to Naggy, (I think I have it figured out where in Perma Vox is...but...lol), and geography seems like an integral part of raid management.<br>
<br>
However, I'd love to help organize, make lists, follow directions, boost morale, all that sort of thing.<br>
<br>
I also think it would be an excellent exercise for us. <p><b>Vainne K'harmicdeva
 ~The Nightblind Bard~
